Package com.microsoft.windowsazure.services.blob.models

Class CreateBlobResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.windowsazure.services.blob.models.CreateBlobResult

  • public class CreateBlobResult
extends java.lang.Object
    A wrapper class for the response returned from a Blob Service REST API Create Blob operation. This is returned by calls to implementations of com.microsoft.windowsazure.services.blob.BlobContract#createPageBlob(String, String, long, CreateBlobOptions) and BlobContract.createBlockBlob(String, String, java.io.InputStream, CreateBlobOptions) .

    See the Put Blob documentation on MSDN for details of the underlying Blob Service REST API operation.
